        section.working-package.text-center.bg-light(id="workingpackages")
            .container
                h2.mb-5 Solutions

                // AP1
                .row.py-5.my-5
                    .col-lg-5.text-start.my-3
                        .package-header(data-aos='fade-right')
                            h3.text-primary AP 1
                            .progress.mt-2.mb-3(style="height: 5px;")
                                .progress-bar.bg-secondary(role='progressbar' style="width: 30%;" aria-valuenow='30' aria-valuemin='0' aria-valuemax='100')
                            h3.text-muted Design digitales Szenario
                        .package-description(data-aos='fade-right', data-aos-delay='300')
                            p Das AP1 legt den Grundstein für die weiteren Arbeiten im Projektverlauf. Hier wurde in Gesprächen mit Industrievertretern ermittelt, was genau die CCP leisten muss, um einen Mehrwert für die beteiligten Unternehmen zu schaffen, wie sich die Plattform gut in bestehende Workflows und Ökosysteme einfügen kann und welche Fehler bei der Umsetzung vermieden werden sollten. Im weiteren Projektverlauf werden die entwickelten Lösungen vorgestellt und weiteres Verbesserungspotential identifiziert.

                            //a.btn.btn-outline-primary.mb-lg-0.mb-5.mt-3(href='#')
                                p.mb-0 Mehr erfahren

                    .col-lg-7.text-lg-end.text-start
                        .package-image(data-aos='fade-left' data-aos-delay='800')
                            img(src='assets/img/wp/1.WebP' alt='AP1')
                
                // AP2
                .row.py-5.my-5
                    .col-lg-5.order-lg-2.text-start.my-3
                        .package-header(data-aos='fade-left')
                            h3.text-primary AP 2
                            .progress.mt-2.mb-3(style="height: 5px;")
                                .progress-bar.bg-secondary(role='progressbar' style="width: 85%;" aria-valuenow='85' aria-valuemin='0' aria-valuemax='100')
                            h3.text-muted Transparency and trust system
                        .package-description(data-aos='fade-left', data-aos-delay='300')
                            p The aim of developing a decentralised platform requires a high degree of trust-creating technology, as it is not possible to establish personal trust with all players. The CCP therefore relies on the exchange of exclusively signed data and an SSI-based trust system.
                            a.btn.btn-outline-primary.mb-lg-0.mb-5.mt-3(href='assets/files/trust.pdf')
                                p.mb-0 Mehr erfahren
                                    // i.bi.bi-info-lg

                    .col-lg-7.order-lg-1.text-lg-start.text-end
                        .package-image(data-aos='fade-right', data-aos-delay='800')
                            img(src='assets/img/wp/2.WebP' alt='AP2')

                // AP3
                .row.py-5.my-5
                    .col-lg-5.text-start.my-3
                        .package-header(data-aos='fade-right')
                            h3.text-primary AP 3
                            .progress.mt-2.mb-3(style="height: 5px;")
                                .progress-bar.bg-secondary(role='progressbar' style="width: 10%;" aria-valuenow='10' aria-valuemin='0' aria-valuemax='100')
                            h3.text-muted Platform (CCP)
                        .package-description(data-aos='fade-right', data-aos-delay='300')
                            p The digital platform connects the various data streams, trust sources and external systems to the COPPA product passport and offers a low entry barrier for stakeholders to the COPPA ecosystem.
                            a.btn.btn-outline-primary.mb-lg-0.mb-5.mt-3(href='https://coppa.praqtics.com/home')
                                p.mb-0 Register here

                    .col-lg-7.text-lg-end.text-start
                        .package-image(data-aos='fade-left', data-aos-delay='800')
                            img(src='assets/img/wp/3.WebP' alt='AP3')


                // AP4
                .row.py-5.my-5
                    .col-lg-5.order-lg-2.text-start.my-3
                        .package-header(data-aos='fade-left')
                            h3.text-primary AP 4
                            .progress.mt-2.mb-3(style="height: 5px;")
                                .progress-bar.bg-secondary(role='progressbar' style="width: 0%;" aria-valuenow='0' aria-valuemin='0' aria-valuemax='100')
                            h3.text-muted Business model
                        .package-description(data-aos='fade-left', data-aos-delay='300')
                            p The platforms business model is developed to be circular, scalable and open. Additionally a common digital language and solutions for data collection and processing, the digital life cycle file for plastics, localisation and typification of plastics and integration of medium-sized companies are developed.

                            //a.btn.btn-outline-primary.mb-lg-0.mb-5.mt-3(href='#')
                                p.mb-0 Mehr erfahren
                                    i.bi.bi-info-lg

                    .col-lg-7.order-lg-1.text-lg-start.text-end
                        .package-image(data-aos='fade-right', data-aos-delay='800')
                            img(src='assets/img/wp/4.WebP' alt='AP4')


                // AP5
                .row.py-5.my-5
                    .col-lg-5.text-start.my-3
                        .package-header(data-aos='fade-right')
                            h3.text-primary AP 5
                            .progress.mt-2.mb-3(style="height: 5px;")
                                .progress-bar.bg-secondary(role='progressbar' style="width: 20%;" aria-valuenow='20' aria-valuemin='0' aria-valuemax='100')
                            h3.text-muted Ecosystem
                        .package-description(data-aos='fade-right', data-aos-delay='300')
                            p As a value creation system, the plastics and packaging industries form their own economic ecosystem that cannot be considered closed at any time. An analysis of the plastics food packaging industry using business ecosystem mapping forms the basis for the subsequent design of the future application ecosystem using ecosystem design methods. Recommendations for action for companies to tap into potential network effects and enter the new application ecosystem are also developed.

                            a.btn.btn-outline-primary.mb-lg-0.mb-5.mt-3(href='ap5.html')
                                p.mb-0 Mehr erfahren

                    .col-lg-7.text-lg-end.text-start
                        .package-image(data-aos='fade-left', data-aos-delay='800')
                            img(src='assets/img/wp/5.WebP' alt='AP5')

                // AP6
                .row.py-5.my-5
                    .col-lg-5.order-lg-2.text-start.my-3
                        .package-header(data-aos='fade-left')
                            h3.text-primary AP 6
                            .progress.mt-2.mb-3(style="height: 5px;")
                                .progress-bar.bg-secondary(role='progressbar' style="width: 0%;" aria-valuenow='0' aria-valuemin='0' aria-valuemax='100')
                            h3.text-muted Carbon Footprint
                        .package-description(data-aos='fade-left', data-aos-delay='300')
